> x pigeon-hole cabinet

> x pigeon-hole cabinet

The departmental pigeon-hole cabinet where the post and  internal messages are placed (and often left for weeks or even years on end), there are individual compartments each labelled with a person's name.

Yours appear to have something in it, it's a note from Professor Weck, it reads "In case your PC isn't working.. I've gone down to the lab, I've had a breakthrough! Meet me there, signed" ...and then there’s Prof's complicated scrawl of a signature.
