You insert several coins into the slot and press the 1st Diet Coke button, a message flashes up next to it saying "Sold Out", you press the 2nd Diet Coke button, there is a satisfying metallic clunk and thud as the can hits the dispensing tray. You pick it up.
> drink coke

> drink coke

You crack open the ring tab, the can gives forth a 'pssst' noise, you drain the can in several swigs, it's oh so familiar sweet cool and dry taste is still awesome, and you can feel the caffeine hitting your brain.

You feel like you can do anything (until the hit wears off and you need another). You belch loudly.
