You are in The Year 2037: Your Office.

You can see a Small Hole and a window.

You can go out.

Your old office now appears to be a storeroom, it's full of broken furniture, boxes of paperwork, old computer parts and electrical components are stacked up. Like the rest of the building there is dust and cobwebs everywhere and the paint is peeling off the walls.

> put cheese in small hole

> put cheese in small hole

You break a small piece off the lump of cheese and place it near the hole, suddenly you see a small nose and whiskers appear, a tiny mouse grabs the cheese with its little front paws,  gobbles it down, then gives a tiny squeak of appreciation.

The mouse steps out of the hole and appears for all the world to be wearing a tiny academic gown, hood and tudor bonnet.

Somewhere from the folds of its gown it produces a tiny business card and holds it up to you, you take it. The mouse bows and scurries off out of sight.
